t=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Italic Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;This text is italic&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-italic\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Underline Text</h2>\r\n<p>The HTML <code>&lt;u&gt;&lt;/u&gt;</code> element is used for <i>underlined</i> text.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Underlined Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;This text is underlined&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-underline\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Mark</h2>\r\n<p>Use the <code>&lt;mark&gt;&lt;/mark&gt;</code> tag if you want to highlight parts of your text.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Mark Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Do not forget to learn &lt;mark&gt;poem&lt;/mark&gt; today.&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-mark\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Strike Text</h2>\r\n<p>The HTML <code>&lt;strike&gt;&lt;/strike&gt;</code> element is displayed with strikethrough. It is a thin line which cross the statement..</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Strike Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strike&gt;This text with strike&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-strike\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Monospaced Font</h2>\r\n<p>If you want that each letter has the same width then you should write the content within <code>&lt;tt&gt;...&lt;/tt&gt;</code> element. Most of the fonts are known as variable-width fonts because different letters are of different widths (for example, the letter \'m\' is wider than the letter \'i\'). In a monospaced font, however, each letter has the same width..</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Monospaced Font Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;tt&gt;My Paragraph in monospaced font.&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-monospaced\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Superscript Text</h2>\r\n<p>The content of a <code>&lt;sup&gt;....&lt;/sup&gt;</code> element is written in superscript, the font size used is the same size as the characters surrounding it but is displayed half a character\'s height above the other characters.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Superscript Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;sup&gt;My Paragraph in Superscript.&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-superscript\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Subscript Text</h2>\r\n<p>The content of a <code>&lt;sub&gt;....&lt;/sub&gt;</code> element is written in superscript, the font size used is the same size as the characters surrounding it but is displayed half a character\'s height below the other characters.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Subscript Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;sub&gt;My Paragraph in Subscript.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-subscript\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Deleted Text</h2>\r\n<p>Anything that puts within <code>&lt;del&gt;...&lt;/del&gt;</code> is displayed as deleted text.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Deleted Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;del&gt;Delete my paragraph.&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-deleted\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Inserted Text</h2>\r\n<p>Anything that puts within <code>&lt;ins&gt;...&lt;/ins&gt;</code> is displayed as inserted text.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Inserted Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;del&gt;Delete my paragraph.&lt;/del&gt;&lt;ins&gt;Write another paragraph.&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-inserted\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Large Text</h2>\r\n<p>The content of the <code>&lt;big&gt;....&lt;/big&gt;</code> element is displayed one font size larger than the rest of the text surrounding it as shown below</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Large Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;big&gt;Write the paragraph in large font.&lt;/big&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-large\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Small Text</h2>\r\n<p>The content of the <code>&lt;small&gt;...&lt;/small&gt;</code> element is displayed one font size smaller than the rest of the text surrounding it as shown below</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Small Text Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;small&gt;Write the paragraph in large font.&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-small\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>',4,1,'HTML Formatting - nexladder','learn html formatting, html tutorial online, html tutorial beginners, professionals, introduction, basic tags, meta tags, attributes, phrase tags, comments, fonts, marquees, lists, images, links, tables, frames, layouts, forms, style sheet and more.','Learn Html in easy and simple steps starting from basic to advanced concepts with tags, elements, tables, forms, anchor, image, heading, textarea, div etc',1,1529739712,'2018-06-23 07:41:52','2018-06-23 07:41:52'),(174,5,30,'HTML Heading','html-heading','<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <p>Headings are defined with the <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> to <code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> tags.<code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> defines the most important heading. <code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> defines the least important heading.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n    <h3>Importance of Headings</h3>\r\n	<ul class=\"points\">\r\n	   <li>Use <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> headings as main headings, followed by <code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> headings, then the less important <code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> headings, and so on.</li>\r\n	   <li>As search engines use headings to index the structure and content of your web pages so use it very wisely in your webpage.</li>\r\n	   <li>Don\'t use headings to make text <strong>BIG</strong> or <strong>bold</strong>. Use it only for highlighting the heading of your document and to show the document structure.</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p> <i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> See this example:</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of HTML headings tag&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n   &lt;h1&gt;Heading 1.&lt;/h1&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n   &lt;h2&gt;Heading 2.&lt;/h2&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n   &lt;h3&gt;Heading 3.&lt;/h3&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n   &lt;h4&gt;Heading 4.&lt;/h4&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n   &lt;h5&gt;Heading 5.&lt;/h5&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n   &lt;h6&gt;Heading 6.&lt;/h6&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></span></span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-heading-tag\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>',5,1,'HTML Heading - nexladder','learn html heading, html tutorial online, html tutorial beginners, professionals, introduction, basic tags, meta tags, attributes, phrase tags, comments, fonts, marquees, lists, images, links, tables, frames, layouts, forms, style sheet and more.','Learn Html in easy and simple steps starting from basic to advanced concepts with tags, elements, tables, forms, anchor, image, heading, textarea, div etc',1,1529740384,'2018-06-23 07:53:04','2018-06-23 07:53:04'),(175,5,30,'HTML Paragraph','html-paragraph','<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <p>HTML paragraph <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> tag is used to define a paragraph in a webpage. It is used to publish text on the web pages.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p> <i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> See this example:</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of HTML Paragraphs&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n   &lt;p&gt;This is a paragraph.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n   &lt;p&gt;This is a another paragraph.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></span></span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-paragraph-tag\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>',6,1,'HTML Paragraph - nexladder','learn html paragraph, html tutorial online, html tutorial beginners, professionals, introduction, basic tags, meta tags, attributes, phrase tags, comments, fonts, marquees, lists, images, links, tables, frames, layouts, forms, style sheet and more.','Learn Html in easy and simple steps starting from basic to advanced concepts with tags, elements, tables, forms, anchor, image, heading, textarea, div etc',1,1529740573,'2018-06-23 07:56:13','2018-06-23 07:56:13'),(176,5,30,'HTML Anchor','html-anchor','<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <p>Links are specified in HTML using the <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> tag. Links allow users to click their way from page to page. You can click on a link and jump to another document. The <strong>\"href\"</strong> attribute is the most important attribute of the HTML <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> tag.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p> <i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> See this example:</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of HTML Links&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n   &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nexladder.com/&quot; title=&quot;Visit Nexladder!&quot;>Visit Nexladder!&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n   &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nexladder.com/html-tutorial&quot; title=&quot;Click for HTML Tutorial!&quot;>Click for HTML Tutorial!&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"tag\">  \r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></span></span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <h3>HTML Links - The target Attribute</h3>\r\n  <p>The <strong>target</strong> attribute specifies where to open the linked document.</p>\r\n  <ul class=\"points\">\r\n	  <li><strong>_blank</strong> - Opens the linked document in a new window or tab</li>\r\n	  <li><strong>_self</strong> - Opens the linked document in the same window/tab as it was clicked (this is default)</li>\r\n	  <li><strong>_parent</strong> - Opens the linked document in the parent frame</li>\r\n	  <li><strong>_top</strong> - Opens the linked document in the full body of the window</li>\r\n	  <li><em>framename</em> - Opens the linked document in a named frame</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-anchor-tag\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>',7,1,'HTML Anchor - nexladder','learn html anchor, html link, html tutorial online, html tutorial beginners, professionals, introduction, basic tags, meta tags, attributes, phrase tags, comments, fonts, marquees, lists, images, links, tables, frames, layouts, forms, style sheet and more.','Learn Html in easy and simple steps starting from basic to advanced concepts with tags, elements, tables, forms, anchor, image, heading, textarea, div etc',1,1529740872,'2018-06-23 08:01:12','2018-06-23 08:04:20'),(177,5,30,'HTML Image','html-image','<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p>HTML <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> tag is used to display image on the web page. The <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> tag is an empty tag, which means that, it can contain only list of attributes and it has no closing tag.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <h3>Attributes of HTML <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> tag</h3>\r\n  <ul class=\"points\">\r\n	  <li><strong>src</strong> - describes the source or path of the image.</li>\r\n	  <li><strong>alt</strong> - defines an alternate text for the image, if it can\'t be displayed. The value of the alt attribute describe the image in words.</li>\r\n	  <li><strong>width</strong> -  It specify the width to display the image.</li>\r\n	  <li><strong>height</strong> - It specifies the height of the image.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p> <i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> See this example:</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of HTML Images&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n   &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://nexladder.com/images/nexlogo.png&quot; src=&quot;&quot; />&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></span></span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-image-tag\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>',8,1,'HTML Image - nexladder','learn html image, html tutorial online, html tutorial beginners, professionals, introduction, basic tags, meta tags, attributes, phrase tags, comments, fonts, marquees, lists, images, links, tables, frames, layouts, forms, style sheet and more.','Learn Html in easy and simple steps starting from basic to advanced concepts with tags, elements, tables, forms, anchor, image, heading, textarea, div etc',1,1529741163,'2018-06-23 08:06:03','2018-06-23 08:06:03'),(178,5,30,'HTML Table','html-table','<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p>HTML table is defined with the <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> tag. It is used to manage the layout of the page e.g. header, body content, footer etc. HTML <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> tag is used to display data in tabular form. There can be many columns in a row. Each table row is defined with the <code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> tag. A table header is defined with the <code>&lt;th&gt;</code> tag. By default, table headings are bold and centered. A table data/cell is defined with the <code>&lt;td&gt;</code> tag.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p> <i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> See this example:</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of HTML Table&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n   &lt;table border=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;thead&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;th&gt;No.&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th&gt;Name&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th&gt;Email&lt;/th&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/thead&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;1&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;Saarthak&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;saarthak@example.com&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;2&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;Vijay&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;vijay@example.com&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></span></span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-table-tag\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>',9,1,'HTML Table - nexladder','learn html table, html tutorial online, html tutorial beginners, professionals, introduction, basic tags, meta tags, attributes, phrase tags, comments, fonts, marquees, lists, images, links, tables, frames, layouts, forms, style sheet and more.','Learn Html in easy and simple steps starting from basic to advanced concepts with tags, elements, tables, forms, anchor, image, heading, textarea, div etc',1,1529741346,'2018-06-23 08:09:06','2018-06-23 08:09:06'),(179,5,30,'HTML Lists','html-lists','<div class=\"content\">\r\n <p>It is used to specify lists of information. All lists must contain one or more list elements. There are three different types of HTML lists :</p>\r\n <ul class=\"points\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 5px\">\r\n   <li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> - Unordered List or Bulleted List (ul) -  All the list items are marked with bullets.</li>\r\n   <li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> - Ordered List or Numbered List (ol) -  All the list items are marked with numbers.</li>\r\n   <li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code> - It is also known as definition list where entries are listed like a dictionary.</li>\r\n </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n <h3>HTML Ordered List or Numbered List</h3>\r\n <p>All the list items are marked with numbers. It is also known as numbered list. The ordered list starts with <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> tag and the list items start with <code>&lt;li&gt;</code> tag.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Below the example of <strong>Ordered List</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of Ordered List&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n   &lt;ol&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;C&lt;/li&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;C++&lt;/li&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;Java&lt;/li&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;Oracle&lt;/li&gt; </span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n	 &lt;li&gt;Php&lt;/li&gt; </span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n  &lt;/ol&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\"> \r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-ordered-list\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n <h3>HTML Unordered List or Bulleted List</h3>\r\n <p>All the list items are marked with bullets. It is also known as bulleted list. The Unordered list starts with <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> tag and the list items start with <code>&lt;li&gt;</code> tag.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Below the example of <strong>Unordered List</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of Unordered List&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n   &lt;ul&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;C&lt;/li&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;C++&lt;/li&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;Java&lt;/li&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">  \r\n	 &lt;li&gt;Oracle&lt;/li&gt; </span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n	 &lt;li&gt;Php&lt;/li&gt; </span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n  &lt;/ul&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\"> \r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-unordered-list\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n <h3>HTML Definition List</h3>\r\n <p>It is supported by HTML and XHTML. It is also known as definition list where entries are listed like a dictionary. The definition list is the ideal way to present a glossary, list of terms, or other <strong>name/value</strong> list.</p> \r\n <p>Definition List makes use of following three tags.</p>\r\n  <ul class=\"points\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 5px\">\r\n   <li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code> - defines the start of the list.</li>\r\n   <li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code> - defines the term.</li>\r\n   <li style=\"list-style-type:none\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code> - defines the term definition (description).</li>\r\n </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Below the example of <strong>Definition List</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Example of Definition List&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;dl&gt;\r\n	 &lt;dt&gt;&lt;b&gt;HTTP&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/dt&gt;\r\n	 &lt;dd&gt;stands for Hyper Text Transfer Protocol&lt;/dd&gt;\r\n	 &lt;dt&gt;&lt;b&gt;HTML&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/dt&gt;\r\n	 &lt;dd&gt;stands for Hyper Text Markup Language&lt;/dd&gt;\r\n  &lt;/dl&gt; \r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-definition-list\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>',10,1,'HTML Lists - nexladder','learn html lists, html tutorial online, html tutorial beginners, professionals, introduction, basic tags, meta tags, attributes, phrase tags, comments, fonts, marquees, lists, images, links, tables, frames, layouts, forms, style sheet and more.','Learn Html in easy and simple steps starting from basic to advanced concepts with tags, elements, tables, forms, anchor, image, heading, textarea, div etc',1,1529741667,'2018-06-23 08:14:27','2018-06-23 08:18:39'),(180,5,30,'HTML Form','html-form','<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <p>The HTML <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> element defines a form that is used to collect different kinds of user inputs such as name, email, contact number etc.</p>\r\n  <p>An HTML form contains elements called controls like input box, check boxes, radio buttons, textarea, submit buttons etc.The <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> tag is used to create an HTML form.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n <table class=\"table table-responsive table-bordered\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n	    <caption class=\"summary\">Form Tags</caption>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		   <th>Tag</th>\r\n		   <th>Description</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		    <td><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></td><td>It defines an HTML form to enter inputs by the used side.</td>\r\n	    </tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		   <td><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></td><td>It defines a label for an input element.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		   <td><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></td><td>It groups the related element in a form.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		   <td><code>&lt;legend&gt;</code></td><td>It defines a caption for a &lt;fieldset&gt; element.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		   <td><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></td><td>It defines an input control.</td></tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		   <td><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></td><td>It defines a multi-line input control.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		   <td><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></td><td>It defines a drop-down list.</td></tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		    <td><code>&lt;optgroup&gt;</code></td><td>It defines a group of related options in a drop-down list.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		    <td><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></td><td>It defines an option in a drop-down list.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		    <td><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></td><td>It defines a clickable button.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML Login Form</h2>\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Below the example of a login form.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML Login Form Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n      &lt;fieldset&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;legend&gt;Log In&lt;/legend&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label&gt;Username: &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label&gt;Password: &lt;input type=&quot;password&quot;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;Submit&quot;&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n      &lt;/fieldset&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-login-form\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML TextField Control</h2>\r\n<p>The <strong>type=\"text\"</strong> attribute of input tag <code>&lt;input /&gt;</code> creates textfield control also known as textfield control. Text fields are one line areas that allow the user to input text.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML Text Field Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label for=&quot;username&quot;&gt;Username:&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;username&quot; id=&quot;username&quot; placeholder=&quot;Enter Username&quot; /&gt;\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-text-field\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML Password Control</h2>\r\n<p>Password fields are similar to text fields. The password is not visible to the user in password field control. The only difference is; characters in a password field are masked i.e. shown as asterisks or dots.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML Password Field Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label for=&quot;password&quot;&gt;Password:&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		&lt;input type=&quot;password&quot; name=&quot;password&quot; id=&quot;password&quot; placeholder=&quot;Enter Password&quot; /&gt;\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-password-field\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML Radio Button Or Option Button Control</h2>\r\n<p>It is used to select one from pre-defined set of options.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;Radio Button Or Option Button Example&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label for=&quot;gender&quot;&gt;Gender:&lt;/label&gt;&lt;br /&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		Male &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;gender&quot; id=&quot;gender&quot; value=&quot;male&quot; /&gt;\r\n		Female &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;gender&quot; id=&quot;gender&quot; value=&quot;female&quot; /&gt;\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-radio-button-control\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML Checkbox Control</h2>\r\n<p>It is used to select one or more option from pre-defined set of options.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML Checkbox Control&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label for=&quot;hobby&quot;&gt;Hobby:&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		Cricket &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; name=&quot;sports&quot; id=&quot;cricket&quot; value=&quot;cricket&quot; /&gt;\r\n		Football &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; name=&quot;sports&quot; id=&quot;football&quot; value=&quot;football&quot; /&gt;\r\n		Tennis &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; name=&quot;sports&quot; id=&quot;tennis&quot; value=&quot;tennis&quot; /&gt;\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-checkbox\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML File Select box</h2>\r\n<p>It enables the user to browse for a file.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML File Select box&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label for=&quot;upload&quot;&gt;File:&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		&lt;input type=&quot;file&quot; name=&quot;file&quot; id=&quot;file&quot; /&gt;\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-file-select-box\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML Textarea</h2>\r\n<p>It is a multiple-line text input control that allows a user to enter more than one line of text.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML Textarea&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;label for=&quot;address&quot;&gt;Address:&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		&lt;textarea rows=&quot;4&quot; cols=&quot;25&quot; name=&quot;address&quot; id=&quot;address&quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-textarea\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML Select Boxes</h2>\r\n<p>A select box is a dropdown list of options that allows user to select one or more option from a pull-down list of options.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML Select Boxes&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;label for=&quot;select&quot;&gt;Country:&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;select&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n        &lt;option&gt;India&lt;/option&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		&lt;option&gt;Sri Lanka&lt;/option&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n		&lt;option&gt;Bangladesh&lt;/option&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;/select&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-select-box\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>HTML Submit and Reset Buttons</h2>\r\n<p>submit button is used to send the form data while reset button resets all the forms control to default values.</p>\r\n<pre class=\"lang-php prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><code><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">lang</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">\r\n</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;title&gt;HTML Submit and Reset Buttons&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/head&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;form action=&quot;#&quot; method=&quot;post&quot;&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n       &lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;Name:&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n       &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;name&quot; id=&quot;name&quot; /&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n       &lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;Submit&quot;&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n       &lt;input type=&quot;reset&quot; value=&quot;Reset&quot;&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n    &lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n &lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</span></code>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n  <a href=\"https://nexladder.com/codemirror/html/html-submit-reset-button\" target=\"_blank\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-code\">Try it Yourself <i 